list.name: Changes
list.comment: - Added presets.h to store all preset arrays of outlines for testing DFS/BFS speed and # of black pixels checked for different shapes, as well as implemented the presets into program for user access - Added color modes, having 9 gradient color options and a rainbow color palette for each iteration so users can visualize in fun, new colors (modified in BFS, DFS, & interface) - Removed "Fill Image" button in lieu of color mode, as image filling is done by clicking the Active Screen

task.summary: - Added interface.h class for UI and implemented functionality of UI & interactions between UI and active screen. - Added DFS option for fill traversal, modified BFS for statistics and additional features, both now have gradient fill to demonstrate iteration visually - Added the ability to update canvas quickly UI interaction - Added the ability to restart canvas to blank white slate for harmonious continuous user interaction - Added two other parametric constructors for certain modes capabilities (different "canvases") - Added Help Menu Screen with all the current and future planned shortcuts and hotkeys for the program - Implemented "Drawing Mode" where you can now draw border pixels that will not fill when using DFS/BFS - Implemented Sparse and Dense "Maze" randomized generated outlines

- Added presets.h to store all preset arrays of outlines for testing DFS/BFS speed and # of black pixels checked for different shapes, as well as implemented the presets into program for user access - Added color modes, having 9 gradient color options and a rainbow color palette for each iteration so users can visualize in fun, new colors (modified in BFS, DFS, & interface) - Removed "Fill Image" button in lieu of color mode, as image filling is done by clicking the Active Screen
